canada retail sale fall 0.1 pct in januari canada 's retail sale , season adjust , fell 0.1 pct in januari after gain 0.9 pct in decemb , statist canada said . retail sale fell to 11.98 billion dlr from 11.99 billion dlr in decemb , 1986. unadjust sale were 6.9 pct higher than in januari , 1986. in januari , automobil sale fell 1.9 pct , depart store sale slip 3.2 pct and varieti store sale plung 14 pct . the declin were offset by a 5.5 pct increa in groceri store sale and a 9.9 pct gain in hardwar sale .